            "title": "Diet of wrinkle-lipped free-tailed bat (Tadarida plicata Buchannan, 1800) in central Thailand: insectivorous bats potentially act as biological pest control agents",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Watcharee",
